							<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 victoria-font" style="color: #2F4858;">
								Economic History
							</h3>
							<p class="text-slate-600 font-sans mb-4">
								Comprehensive studies on how economies and financial systems have evolved over time.
							</p>
							<ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 font-sans space-y-1">
