							</h3>
							<p class="text-slate-600 font-sans text-center mb-6">
								Historical market performance, asset class returns, and economic indicators.
							</p>
							<div class="text-center">
								<span class="font-sans inline-block bg-gray-400 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg">
