							<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 victoria-font" style="color: #2F4858;">
								Historical Statistics
							</h3>
							<p class="text-slate-600 font-sans text-sm mb-3">
								Long-term economic and financial data from official sources.
							</p>
							<a href="#" class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #9e383d;">
